ğŸ“ Easy Explanation
ğŸ”¹ Package
Groups related classes
Avoids name conflict
ğŸ”¹ Sub-package
Package inside another package
Written using dot (.)
Copy code
Java
package mypackage.advanced;
ğŸ”¹ Inheritance
ScientificCalculator extends Calculator
Can use add() and subtract() methods
ğŸ”‘ One-Line Exam Answer
A package groups related classes, and a sub-package is a package inside another package, accessed using dot notation.
